introduction: Married to Medicine's hit franchise ventures to the Lone Star State for "Married to Medicine: Houston."Home to the largest medical community in the country, Houston provides the backdrop for a thriving group of physicians and wives of doctors looking to advance their medical careers and expand their enviable lifestyles.Married to Medicine Houston follows five dynamic women on the rise as they face high stakes in both their social circle and the medical world. These doctors and wives of doctors appear to have it all: they are educated, attractive, and polished professionals, but beneath the surface, viewers will see major obstacles that threaten their upward momentum. After putting their lives on hold to be a physician or a dedicated wife, the ladies must navigate marriage, children, family, and Houston society. Will these powerful females prove that they truly can rise to the top as they struggle to juggle it all?
